{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "铁震天、谢玉宝、俞六进入死谷地下密室，发现这里没有黄金、宫室和失踪马车，只有泥石砌成的床桌椅，却有湘绣丝棉被和波斯水晶灯。灯亮后，床上露出一具花白头发的枯骨，背后被削尖竹刺穿心，显然在熟睡中遭熟人或轻功高手暗算。谢玉宝依据母亲所述旧闻和尸骨四十颗牙齿，断定死者才是真无十三。由此众人推知先前的无十三是假冒者，因为死谷无黄金，也无人见过真无十三。正当铁震天追问冒充动机时，地室中忽然传来第四个人轻远的声音，称这出戏似乎该演完了。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人就是无十三。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你说这个死人就是无十三？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "绝对是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你怎么看出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他到碧玉山庄去过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "那时候你出世了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "那时候你还没出世，怎么能看得到他？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "就算你以前见过他，现在也没法子认出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虽然我没有见过他，也一样能认得出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我母亲曾经跟我说过有关他的很多事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只凭其中一件事，我就能认出他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "一件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "哪件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "牙齿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "牙齿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，牙齿，",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人的容貌虽然会改变，牙齿却绝不会改变的，而且每个人的牙齿长得都不一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我母亲常说：天下牙齿长得最奇怪的人，就是无十三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "他的牙齿有什么奇怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他的牙齿比别人多四颗，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他有三十八颗牙齿，加上智慧齿就是四十颗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你以前有没有见过长了四十颗牙齿的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已经数过，数了两遍。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我才能确定他就是无十三。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "如果这个死人就是无十三。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "那个无十三是谁呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是假的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "假的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里根本就没有黄金，无十三也根本不可能找到那么多人为他效力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以那个无十三当然是假的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况谁也没有见过无十三，谁也看不出他是真是假，每个人都可以冒充他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "为什么要冒充他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_di_si_ge_ren",
      "speaker_name": "第四个人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们这出戏，是不是已经应该演完了？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    }
